parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbag to deploy unexpectedly, leading to injuries or fatalities, or fail to deploy in the event of a crash, increasing the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The SRS (Supplemental Restraint System) light is illuminated on the dashboard
the airbag fails to deploy in the event of a crash.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Unintended Acceleration due to Throttle Malfunction
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden and unintended acceleration of the vehicle can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries, posing a significant risk to the safety of the driver and passengers.
symptoms: sudden acceleration when shifting into drive gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause a loss of critical vehicle functions, including lights, gauges, and safety systems, which can increase the risk of accidents or leave the driver stranded. In severe cases, it can lead to electrical fires, which can cause damage to the vehicle and potentially harm occupants.
symptoms: The brake light indicator flashes on the dashboard
smoke coming from the air vents

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the cooling system can cause engine overheating, leading to damage to the engine, cylinder head, and other components, which can result in costly repairs, engine failure, and potentially cause accidents due to loss of power or stalling.
symptoms: sweet or burning smell from the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of engine gaskets can cause coolant or oil leaks, leading to engine damage, overheating, and potentially cause accidents due to loss of power or stalling.
symptoms: sweet or burning smell from the engine

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power seat wiring can cause a short circuit, leading to a fire, which can result in damage to the vehicle and potentially harm the occupants.
symptoms: The power seats malfunction or stop working
the wiring under the seat melts or burns
the plastic casing of the seat melts or deforms
the seat adjusts unexpectedly or erratically.
